          "title": "WHAT'S THE FUTURE OF PMS?",
          "summary": "The surge of AI hype and tool obsession is pushing PMs toward quick fixes and away from the fundamentals that matter. Strong product work still depends on clear thinking, strategy, alignment, and deep problem understanding. AI should support those efforts instead of replacing them.",
